spec_data.Name: perl-MooX-StrictConstructor
spec_data.Description:
Simply loading this module makes your constructors "strict". If your
constructor is called with an attribute init argument that your class does
not declare, then it dies. This is a great way to catch small typos.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:58:14 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Make your Moo-based object constructors blow up on unknown attributes
